Of course, Dickie's idea
of music is jazz.

36
00:02:20,797 --> 00:02:23,134
- Oh, dear.
- He has a saxophone.

37
00:02:23,217 --> 00:02:26,179
To my ear,
jazz is just noise.

38
00:02:26,263 --> 00:02:28,390
Just an insolent noise.

39
00:02:28,432 --> 00:02:31,436
- Very nice to meet you.
- And you.

40
